Title: Ian's Shoelace Site – Granny Knot Info
Description: Many people are tying a “Granny Knot”, which sits crooked and comes loose. Learn the “one simple trick” for keeping your shoes neatly and securely tied.

Title: Optional chaining (?.) - JavaScript
Description:
The optional chaining operator (?.)
  enables you to read the value of a property located deep within a chain of connected objects
  without having to check that each reference in the chain is valid.

Title: Zenreader: A 4.7 inches E-Ink RSS Reader Powered by ESP32
Description: I have been long wanting a PDA of sorts with an E-Ink screen that allows me to read stuff on the Internet without eye strains. But the Kindle really sucks as a newsreader device because the experimental browser never works correctly.
